    title: 'The Technical SEO Audit Is Dead. Here\'s What Comes Next.',
    excerpt: 'Crawl health and title tags are table stakes. The new audit disciplines — machine trust, retrieval simulation, entity intelligence — are where competitive advantage now lives.',
